No longer maintained

Name: Hand Mouse
Version: 1.0
Date: 18/06/2010
Category: Mouse Functionalities

Description:
-----------
The Code deals with replacement of mouse functionality using hand gestures

Requirements: 
------------
Software:
1. OpenCV library
2. X11 library - Xlib

Hardware:
1. WebCam

Installation:
------------
The main source file is HandGesture.cpp

Compilation:
-----------
Compile it using the following command
g++ `pkg-config opencv --cflags --libs` HandGesture.cpp -o HandMouse
OR
simply type 'make'(with out quotes) at command line

Works on Linux. I've tested it with ubuntu




 
